        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.6em;">
          &#8226; <strong>[TOSEM]</strong> Code comments for quantum software development kits: An empirical study on Qiskit.
          <CitationCount paperId="mrf-JvkAAAAJ:Y0pCki6q_DkC" />
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.6em;">
