        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5em;">&#8226; <strong>[SQJ 2025]</strong> Evaluating the effectiveness of neuron coverage metrics: a metamorphic-testing approach. <CitationCount paperId="mrf-JvkAAAAJ:Tyk-4Ss8FVUC" /></li>
