          <p style="margin-left: 1.25rem; font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-top: 0.25em;">
            A structured <strong>LaTeX Template</strong> for drafting response letters during peer-review with professional, aesthetic formatting.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
